# Laravel Multi Auth Guard

## When to use

- Configuring multiple auth guards with separate tables (admin, user, member)
- Creating separate login pages and dashboards per user type
- Setting up guards, providers, and password reset brokers in `config/auth.php`
- Building custom middleware for multi-guard authentication

